4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning Bootcamp designed for beginners with no prior experience. This immersive program lasts 16 weeks, featuring three classes per week in a small group setting (maximum of 12 students). Participants will learn Python, SQL, key statistical methods, and develop predictive models using tools such as Pandas and Numpy. The curriculum covers both supervised and unsupervised learning models, industry-standard tools, and includes hands-on projects. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. Courses are available in English or Spanish. For additional details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop